SimpleMimics Usage Permissions

Copyright (c) 2026 AkaneDev

All Rights Reserved.

Permission is granted to use this mod in the following ways:

- Modpacks
- Videos
- Streams
- VODs

Videos

For videos, credit to AkaneDev is required. Credit may be provided in any
reasonable way, including but not limited to:

- A pinned comment
- A mention in the video
- A link to the mod page in the description
- Mentioning the mod name and author in the description

Streams

For livestreams, credit to AkaneDev is required. Credit may be provided in
any reasonable way, including but not limited to:

- Mentioning the mod during the stream
- Including the mod name and author in the stream description
- Linking the mod page in the stream description
- Using a chat command or other chat-based credit system

VODs

VODs are treated differently from live streams and videos. Credit is not
required for VODs, but it is greatly appreciated.

Examples of appreciated credit include:

- A link to the mod page in the description
- Mentioning the mod name and author
- Adding the mod to a list of mods used

Modpacks

If this mod is included in a modpack, the mod must be listed in the
modpack description with credit given to AkaneDev.

Restrictions

You may not:

- Redistribute this mod or modified versions of this mod without permission.
- Reupload this mod to other platforms without permission.
- Use the source code, assets, or systems from this mod in other projects
  without permission.

Exceptions may be granted for educational purposes, such as learning,
research, code review, or personal study. Educational use does not include
creating, distributing, or publishing derivative projects based on this mod.

This software is provided "AS IS", without warranty of any kind, express or
implied. In no event shall the authors or copyright holders be liable for
any claim, damages, or other liability arising from the use of this software.

Thank you for supporting SimpleMimics.
